# Phase 2 & 3 Walkthrough — Real Blockchain Integration

## What Changed

### Before (Phases 0-1)
```
User Action → Express API → MySQL → Done
(Blockchain code existed but was NEVER called)
```

### After (Phases 2-3)
```
User Action → FCL → Flow Blockchain → Sealed → Express API → MySQL Index
(Blockchain is source of truth, MySQL is read cache)
```

---

## Phase 2: Blockchain Integration

### New Files Created

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [placeBid.js](file:///f:/Collage/Sem4/PBL/project1/TenderFloww/client/src/Transactions/placeBid.js) | On-chain bid placement via `BiddingCollection.placeBid()` |
| [settleBidding.js](file:///f:/Collage/Sem4/PBL/project1/TenderFloww/client/src/Transactions/settleBidding.js) | On-chain settlement — NFT transfer + token settlement |
| [flowService.js](file:///f:/Collage/Sem4/PBL/project1/TenderFloww/client/src/services/flowService.js) | Centralized blockchain service layer |

### Files Modified

| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| [getProjectStatuses.js](file:///f:/Collage/Sem4/PBL/project1/TenderFloww/client/src/Scripts/getProjectStatuses.js) | Fixed address (`0x01` → `0xea0627a8b29d7901`), top-level await, missing args |
| [FlowProvider.jsx](file:///f:/Collage/Sem4/PBL/project1/TenderFloww/client/src/context/FlowProvider.jsx) | Added `txInProgress`, `txError`, [clearTx](file:///f:/Collage/Sem4/PBL/project1/TenderFloww/client/src/context/FlowProvider.jsx#43-50); fixed undefined `txId` crash |
| [Modal.jsx](file:///f:/Collage/Sem4/PBL/project1/TenderFloww/client/src/components/modal/Modal.jsx) | Blockchain-first tender creation with multi-step progress UI |
| [Bids.jsx](file:///f:/Collage/Sem4/PBL/project1/TenderFloww/client/src/containers/bids/Bids.jsx) | Blockchain-first bid placement, on-chain status display, explorer links |
| [Tender.jsx](file:///f:/Collage/Sem4/PBL/project1/TenderFloww/client/src/components/tender/Tender.jsx) | Blockchain-first settlement with NFT transfer, explorer links |

### Data Flow (After Phase 2)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant Blocto as Blocto Wallet
    participant Flow as Flow Blockchain
    participant Backend as Express API
    participant MySQL

    User->>Frontend: Place Bid
    Frontend->>Blocto: Sign Transaction
    Blocto->>Flow: Execute placeBid()
    Flow-->>Frontend: TX Sealed ✅
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /placebid (index)
    Backend->>MySQL: INSERT (cache)
    Frontend->>User: Show TX hash + Explorer link
```

