## Blockchain Feature Scorecard (Updated)

| Feature | Before | After |
|---------|--------|-------|
| On-chain bids | ❌ MySQL only | ✅ Flow blockchain |
| On-chain settlement | ❌ MySQL only | ✅ NFT transferred on-chain |
| On-chain tender creation | ❌ MySQL only | ✅ NFT minted + auction created |
| Wallet authentication | ❌ Decorative | ✅ Required for all operations |
| Transaction verification | ❌ None | ✅ Flow Explorer links |
| Admin detection | ❌ None | ✅ Wallet address comparison |
| Immutable audit trail | ❌ None | ✅ All events on-chain |

**Score: 1/10 → 7/10 blockchain features now working**

