## Next Steps (Manual Testing)

1. Start MySQL and run migration
2. Start backend: `cd backend && npm run dev`
3. Start frontend: `cd client && npm run dev`
4. Connect Blocto wallet on `/login`
5. Test tender creation on `/admin` (requires admin wallet)
6. Test bid placement on `/bids?tender_id=<id>`
7. Test settlement after auction expires
